Highlights

   Group awards

   – Qiankun Liu received a best student paper award for his presentation
   in SPIE Photonic Europe, april 2018 Read more

   – Elena Durán Valdeiglesias and Vladyslav Vakarin received awards for
   their posters presented in the Silicon Photonics summer school 2016 in
   Ghent Read more

   – Vladyslav Vakarin received the Best Student presentation at Photonics
   Europe 2016 (Brussels)

   – Diego Perez Galacho received the Best Student Poster Award in the
   Group IV Photonics 2015 in Vancouver.

   – Delphine Marris-Morini, assistant professor at the University Paris
   Sud, received the Bronze medal 2013 from CNRS – Read more

   – Melissa Ziebell, PhD student on silicon modulator, awarded an SPIE
   Scholarship in Optics and Photonics in 2012 – Read more

   – Papichaya Chaisakul received best student paper award from SPIE
   Photonics Europe on Ge/SiGe optoelectronic devices in 2012

   – Etienne Gaufres, PhD student on carbon nanotubes, received
   Arconati-Visconti de la chancellerie award from Paris Universities in
   2011



   Exemple of recent results

   “Experimental GVD engineering in slow light slot photonic crystal
   waveguides” published in Scientific Reports (2016)
